OL,3,CVictim of Laos alcohol poisoning warns
OL,4,Cholidaymakers of dangers
OL,6,FBethany Clarke, a survivor of alcohol
OL,7,Fpoisoning, has joined calls urging
OL,8,Fholidaymakers to be aware of the
OL,9,Fdangers of counterfeit and
OL,10,Fcontaminated drinks.
OL,12,FIn 2024, a British woman, Simone
OL,13,FWhite, and four other tourists died in
OL,14,FLaos after suspected methanol
OL,15,Fpoisoning. Several others, including
OL,16,FMs Clarke, were taken to hospital.
