OL,3,CVictim of Laos alcohol poisoning warns
OL,4,Cholidaymakers of dangers
OL,6,FIn a renewed effort to raise awareness
OL,7,Fof the harms of laced drinks, Ms
OL,8,FClarke told ITV News: "You assume that
OL,9,Fyou're getting the brand you think
OL,10,Fyou're getting, but unfortunately they
OL,11,Fcan just refill with something
OL,12,Fcompletely different.
OL,14,F"The alcohol industry is not regulated
OL,15,Fin a lot of countries."
OL,17,FMs Clarke shared her tips on how to
OL,18,Fspot the symptoms of methanol poisoning
