OL,3,CVictim of Laos alcohol poisoning warns
OL,4,Cholidaymakers of dangers
OL,6,FIt comes as a group of MPs wants
OL,7,Fstronger warnings from the government
OL,8,Fand the travel industry.
OL,10,FLiberal Democrat MP Tom Morrison is
OL,11,Fone of 20 MPs now demanding stronger
OL,12,Fwarnings about the potentially lethal
OL,13,Frisks of bootleg booze on holiday.
OL,15,FHe told ITV News: "There aren't enough
OL,16,Fwarnings. The government has some
OL,17,Fadvice on its website, but it's not
OL,18,Fprominent enough.
