OL,3,CVictim of Laos alcohol poisoning warns
OL,4,Cholidaymakers of dangers
OL,6,FITV News asked the travel agents
OL,7,Fassociation whether it could do more
OL,8,Fto get warnings out.
OL,10,FEmma Brennan of ABTA told us, "We do
OL,11,Fhave specific information on methanol
OL,12,Fon our website, but we also know it's
OL,13,Freally important that people read the
OL,14,Fofficial information from the
OL,15,Fgovernment.
OL,17,F"Our members sell organised travel, a
OL,18,Flot of people who are going to these
OL,19,Fcountries affected where this is an
OL,20,Fissue, are actually backpacking."
